  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "N+ is a port of the original Adobe Flash based PC game, N, to console and handheld systems with new features.\n\n\"N+ is a peerless action-puzzle platformer with more than 300 levels in which to hone your ninja reflexes, plus a built-in level editor for when you're hungry for more. N+ also features unique, physics-based controls, stylish graphics, unlimited lives, competitive and cooperative multiplayer, plenty of gold, and several flavors of sweet, sweet action.\"\n\n\"N+ features N doesn't have:\n-Redesigned graphics and visual effects: a more detailed version of N's in-your-face minimalist style\n-New objects and enemies: Pulse Drone, Laser Turret and Zap Doors\n-Background music and next-gen 5.1 surround sound\n-Way over 400 all-new levels\n-3 pants-wettingly good modes of multiplayer: Co-op, Race and Survival\"",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"In a futuristic world of inadvertently homicidal robots, a daring ninja must use deft acrobatic skill and guts of steel to survive.\"",
      "lang": "en",
